target.echo:
This installs the message center tool.  Targets in this file should not be invoked directly
but should be called by the master build.xml.
The default values for the message center build are given below.  They are usually overridden by 
a properties file.

messagecenter.install.skip = ${messagecenter.install.skip}
messagecenter.svnurl = ${messagecenter.svnurl}
messagecenter.revision = ${messagecenter.revision}
